#Prevention Checklist

Stay Safe Online – Prevention Checklist:
1. Never share OTP, passwords, or banking details with anyone.
2. Always check the website URL before entering sensitive information.
3. Avoid clicking on unknown or suspicious links in emails or messages.
4. Enable two-factor authentication (2FA) on all important accounts.
5. Use strong and unique passwords for different platforms.
6. Do not use public Wi-Fi for online transactions.
7. Carefully verify UPI payment requests before approving them.
8. Keep your devices and apps updated regularly.
9. Install antivirus software for additional security.
10. Immediately report cybercrime on cybercrime.gov.in.

